  <!-- ============= Limitations =========================== -->
  <sect1 id="&appn;-bugs">
    <title>Known Bugs and Limitations</title>

    <para>
      <itemizedlist>
	<listitem>Parameter Entities (ie. entities for use in DTDs)
	  in the internal DTD subset are dereferenced (ie. replaced by their
	  replacement text), you see the result after saving and
	  reloading.</listitem>
	<listitem>General Entities (ie. entities for use in the document
	  content) are not handled transparently by XSLT. They are replaced by
	  their replacement text and should be avoided from the
	  beginning.</listitem>
	<listitem>Memleaks are likely</listitem>
	<listitem>Some deprecated and/or private fields/functions of GTK+,
	  libgnomeui and libbonoboui are used</listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </para>
  </sect1>

